dbus-mqtt-bridge (0.1.0-2) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. (Closes: #XXXXXX)
  * Features:
    - Bidirectional D-Bus to MQTT bridge
    - Support for system and session bus
    - YAML-based configuration
    - Systemd integration with security hardening
    - Runs as unprivileged user with D-Bus policy restrictions
  * Security:
    - Dedicated system user (dbus-mqtt-bridge)
    - Comprehensive systemd hardening
    - D-Bus policy-based access control
    - Service disabled by default, requires configuration

